---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Tyermans Body Shop has been serving Burbank, CA since 1948. Learn about our history and team."
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Est. 1948</p>
      <h1>Problem Solvers<br />Since 1948</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        For over 75 years, Tyermans has been the shop Burbank trusts to make
        things right — from fender benders to ground-up restorations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="inner two-col">
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Tyermans Body Shop opened its doors on West Magnolia Boulevard in 1948.
          What started as a small family operation grew into one of the most
          respected auto body shops in the San Fernando Valley — built on a simple
          promise: fix it right the first time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Decades of hands-on experience mean we've seen everything from minor
          door dings to complete chassis rebuilds. Every car that comes through
          our doors gets the same attention, whether it's a daily driver or a
          weekend show car.
        </p>
        <p>
          We work with all makes and models, handle insurance claims, and keep
          you informed every step of the way. No surprises — just straight talk
          and quality work.
        </p>

        <p>
          At Tyermans, we adhere to all cars both older and newer models. Below
          is a list of services we offer:
        </p>

        <h2>Services</h2>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li>Suspension</li>
          <li>Steering</li>
          <li>Alignment</li>
          <li>Tune-up</li>
          <li>Engine</li>
          <li>Diagnostics &amp; Repairs</li>
          <li>Brakes</li>
          <li>Tires</li>
          <li>Balancing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Special Services</h2>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li>Performance Tuning</li>
          <li>Brake &amp; Suspension Upgrades</li>
          <li>Electrical Upgrades</li>
          <li>Detailing</li>
          <li>Custom Fabrications &amp; Welding</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Shop Info</h3>
        <dl>
          <dt>Address</dt>
          <dd>
            1420 West Magnolia Blvd<br />
            Burbank, CA 91506
          </dd>
          <dt>Phone</dt>
          <dd><a href="tel:+18188467291">(818) 846-7291</a></dd>
          <dt>Email</dt>
          <dd><a href="mailto:Joel@tyermans.com">Joel@tyermans.com</a></dd>
          <dt>Hours</dt>
          <dd>
            Mon – Fri: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM<br />
            Sat – Sun: Closed
          </dd>
        </dl>
        <a href="/#schedule" class="cta-btn">Book an Appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);

    & .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    & h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    & .lead {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 560px;
    }
  }

  /* ── Body ── */
  .about-body {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 6rem;

    & .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;

      @media (max-width: 860px) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    & .content {
      & h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;

        &:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
      }

      & p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.75;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
    }

    & .services-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;

      & li {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        padding-left: 1rem;
        position: relative;

        &::before {
          content: "—";
          position: absolute;
          left: 0;
          color: var(--accent);
        }
      }
    }
  }

  /* ── Info card ── */
  .info-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;

    & h3 {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    & dl {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    & dt {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    & dd {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;

      & a {
        color: var(--text);
        transition: color 0.2s;

        &:hover { color: var(--accent); }
      }
    }

    & .cta-btn {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;

      &:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); }
    }
  }
</style>
